<main>
  <h1>skills</h1>
  <p class="sub">Active skills load in Claude Code everywhere; archived ones sit in <b>archive/</b> and don't. Groups are nested folders — members get auto-managed <b>&lt;group&gt;-&lt;name&gt;</b> links so Claude Code finds them. Everything is plain files — review &amp; commit with git as usual.</p>
  <div id="link" class="banner" hidden></div>
